        "primary": {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "heading2",
              "text": "Designing Identity into Dining",
              "spans": []
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "ANA was conceived as a living cultural canvas, reflecting the UAE’s diversity and Emirati hospitality. The façade features a “no-logo logo” wall, where every version of “ANA / أنا” represents a different personality and identity. This symbolism mirrors the UAE as a melting pot of cultures, translated into Emirati-fusion cuisine, interior design, and a holistic guest experience. The design balances contemporary Arabesque aesthetics with modern luxury — refined materials, warm tones, and bold art statements. From dining areas to the majlis event zone, every detail reinforces ANA’s philosophy of celebrating individuality through shared experience.",
              "spans": []
            }
          ]
        },
        "items": []
